commit.message: Updates the readme.
Two tiny bug fixes.
Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/WilliamRADFunk/irl-reporting-site
Uses screen height for map height, which takes better advantage of larger screens.
Makes the time panel a little more responsive design friendly.
Minor tweaks.
Uses cooler icons to make the markers more informative.
Facilitates name and url change to the site.
Removes superfluous images.
Populates the map with basic icons and colored circles.
Implements week and month resolvers.
Properly uses the resolver to get data for map component.
Starts to implement data service and the map page resolvers.
Adds the favico of the logo.
Adds a nice photo for the About page.
Some cleanups.
Implements side navigation panel for time range on map.
Puts map on the page.
Implements simple about page and initial routing.
Creates the boilerplate template for the web browser portion of the Hack the Indian River Lagoon project.
Initial commit
